pr_review_comment_body:
So if you follow my suggestion above, we'll be keying background-color off of whether the series is active. So something like:

    background-color: {{series.active ? series.color | "grey"}}

I'd also like to add a css class here conditional on the series not being active which turns the text and the border into a lighter shade of grey, to more clearly indicate that it's not active.
